  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Modifies Attack, Multiple Attack, Flurry of Attacks, Multiple Throw, or Throw while Running.<br data-start=\"112\" data-end=\"115\" />Deals half damage.</p><p data-start=\"168\" data-end=\"411\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node>Triggers a vs test of Dexterity against target's Perception Test.</p><p data-start=\"168\" data-end=\"411\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node>On attacker's success, the target loses 1 Reaction.<br data-start=\"262\" data-end=\"265\" />On a hit, attacker gains a +10% bonus to the Test.<br data-start=\"306\" data-end=\"309\" />On a Critical Hit, attacker gains a +30% bonus to the Test.<br data-start=\"359\" data-end=\"362\" />On a Critical Failure, the Test is not triggered.<br /><br />Cost applies to each attack.</p>",
